<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 04:08:20 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>三名哈马斯人质被以色列国防军误杀后，数百人在特拉维夫抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article-live/.premium/hundreds-protest-in-tel-aviv-after-three-hamas-hostages-mistakenly-killed-by-idf/0000018c-707c-d798-adac-f4ff14b20000</link><description>以色列国防军：军队在加沙北部误杀了三名人质 ■ 以色列国防军从加沙打捞出三名人质尸体，其中包括两名以色列国防军士兵 ■ 航运巨头马士基在胡塞武装袭击中暂停红海交通 ■ 美国国家安全顾问表示，战争将持续下去几个月后，将转向分阶段针对以色列访问的哈马斯领导层 ■ 自10月7日以来，以色列境内至少有1,200名平民和士兵被杀；加沙仍有超过 138 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙有 18,608 人死亡、50,594 人受伤</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 02:52:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article-live/.premium/hundreds-protest-in-tel-aviv-after-three-hamas-hostages-mistakenly-killed-by-idf/0000018c-707c-d798-adac-f4ff14b20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列可以从纽约 9/11 清理和纪念活动中学到什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-israel-can-learn-from-new-yorks-9-11-cleanup-and-commemoration/0000018c-6f95-db38-a9fc-efb71e8b0000</link><description>以色列不应该清除南部 10 月 7 日灾难的废墟，而应该学习纽约在 9 月 11 日之后所做的事情</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 23:20:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-israel-can-learn-from-new-yorks-9-11-cleanup-and-commemoration/0000018c-6f95-db38-a9fc-efb71e8b0000</guid></item><item><title>如果定居者的暴力还不够，以色列现在正在剥夺约旦河谷巴勒斯坦人的水源</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2023-12-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/if-settler-violence-wasnt-enough-israel-now-deprives-jordan-valley-palestinians-of-water/0000018c-6f70-dbd5-a39c-ff7344530000</link><description>自战争爆发以来，约 20 个巴勒斯坦家庭因定居者暴力加剧而被迫离开约旦河谷的家园。与此同时，军队不让牧羊人社区获得水源。以色列志愿者日夜努力保护他们</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 22:24:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2023-12-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/if-settler-violence-wasnt-enough-israel-now-deprives-jordan-valley-palestinians-of-water/0000018c-6f70-dbd5-a39c-ff7344530000</guid></item><item><title>随着“后天”政府前景的临近，巴勒斯坦舞台在两极之间摇摆不定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-arena-swings-between-poles-as-prospect-of-day-after-government-looms/0000018c-6cef-d798-adac-ecefe2e80000</link><description>哈马斯领导人最近的声明并不适合以色列人的耳朵，哈马斯不是也不必成为与以色列就解决加沙问题进行谈判的伙伴。伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚和穆萨·阿布·马尔祖克的言论针对巴勒斯坦人</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 22:10:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-arena-swings-between-poles-as-prospect-of-day-after-government-looms/0000018c-6cef-d798-adac-ecefe2e80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的“非殖民化”或巴勒斯坦人的“决定性失败”：这是我们唯一的选择吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/decolonization-of-israel-or-total-defeat-of-palestinians-are-these-our-only-options/0000018c-6f0f-d692-a9dc-7f9f1b040000</link><description>暴行铭刻在两国人民的历史记忆中。领导人实时谈论“以色列的毁灭”和“2023 年加沙浩劫”。在把我们全部吐出来之前，这个地球能吸收多少血？</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 21:43:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/decolonization-of-israel-or-total-defeat-of-palestinians-are-these-our-only-options/0000018c-6f0f-d692-a9dc-7f9f1b040000</guid></item><item><title>就连左派也喜欢以色列的“好阿拉伯人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/even-the-leftists-are-loving-israels-good-arabs/0000018c-6eb5-dbd5-a39c-fff7d7d20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 21:22:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/even-the-leftists-are-loving-israels-good-arabs/0000018c-6eb5-dbd5-a39c-fff7d7d20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列抗议者因加沙人质问题与联合国秘书长对峙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-protesters-confront-un-chief-over-hostages-held-in-gaza/0000018c-6ec2-d798-adac-eeeffd430000</link><description>人质被拖至加沙两个多月后，抗议者指责联合国秘书长安东尼奥·古特雷斯未能履行职责</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 20:28:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-protesters-confront-un-chief-over-hostages-held-in-gaza/0000018c-6ec2-d798-adac-eeeffd430000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队表示，他们在加沙北部杀害了三名人质，并被误认为是威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-killed-three-hostages-mistakenly-identified-as-threat-in-northern-gaza/0000018c-6edd-dbd5-a39c-ffff08470000</link><description>逃离囚禁并被以色列军队杀害的三名人质是 24 岁的 Samer Fuad El-Talalka、28 岁的 Yotam Haim 和 26 岁的 Alon Shamriz</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 20:15:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-killed-three-hostages-mistakenly-identified-as-threat-in-northern-gaza/0000018c-6edd-dbd5-a39c-ffff08470000</guid></item><item><title>“10 月 7 日发生的事情羞辱了以色列的男子气概。回应是暴力”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-happened-on-october-7-humiliated-israeli-masculinity-the-response-is-violence/0000018c-68bb-de43-affd-fcbb5fe40000</link><description>美国心理学家、女权主义学者卡罗尔·吉利根 (Carol Gilligan) 帮助改变了人们对女性道德观念的思考。她对男女关系的见解也与加沙战争有关</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 19:58:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-happened-on-october-7-humiliated-israeli-masculinity-the-response-is-violence/0000018c-68bb-de43-affd-fcbb5fe40000</guid></item><item><title>为什么很少有巴勒斯坦电影讲述加沙的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-so-few-palestinian-films-tell-the-story-of-gaza/0000018c-6eb4-db38-a9fc-efb65b370000</link><description>20 世纪 90 年代烧毁电影院的狂热分子；前往西岸寻找机会的电影制片人；哈马斯政权完全蔑视西方文化——所有这些都阻止了巴勒斯坦电影在大银幕上描绘加沙的生活。只有几部电影能够讲述一些故事</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 19:06:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-so-few-palestinian-films-tell-the-story-of-gaza/0000018c-6eb4-db38-a9fc-efb65b370000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内阁批准战争开始以来首次通过凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点进入加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-approves-entry-of-aid-to-gaza-through-kerem-shalom-crossing/0000018c-6df6-db38-a9fc-edf610910000</link><description>美国安全顾问沙利文对这一在美国重压下获得批准的举措表示欢迎，并表示“我们希望这一新开放将缓解拥堵，并有助于促进救生援助的交付”</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 16:50:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-approves-entry-of-aid-to-gaza-through-kerem-shalom-crossing/0000018c-6df6-db38-a9fc-edf610910000</guid></item><item><title>美国反犹太主义特使呼吁世界对哈马斯屠杀反应不一</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/u-s-antisemitism-envoy-calls-out-worlds-mixed-response-to-hamas-massacre/0000018c-6df8-db38-a9fc-edfa135a0000</link><description>黛博拉·利普斯塔特说，否认大屠杀花了几十年才产生影响。她告诉《国土报》，哈马斯同情者只需要四五天</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 16:34:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/u-s-antisemitism-envoy-calls-out-worlds-mixed-response-to-hamas-massacre/0000018c-6df8-db38-a9fc-edfa135a0000</guid></item><item><title>红海岸线：也门胡塞武装袭击的所有船只</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/red-sea-shipping-yemen-houthis-ships-attacked/0000018c-5df7-d6f9-afbc-5dff7a430000</link><description>在伊朗的支持下，也门胡塞武装使用巡航导弹、无人机和反舰弹道导弹瞄准以色列人拥有的船只或他们确定正在前往以色列的船只</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 16:17:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/red-sea-shipping-yemen-houthis-ships-attacked/0000018c-5df7-d6f9-afbc-5dff7a430000</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装加大对红海船只的攻击力度，但国际社会对此反应甚少</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/houthis-ramp-up-attacks-on-ships-in-red-sea-with-little-international-response/0000018c-6d6a-de43-affd-fd6ad2b60000</link><description>周四，两艘外国商船在红海和阿拉伯海遭到袭击。据报道，周五，胡塞武装继续向国际海上贸易施压，另一艘船在该地区遭到袭击</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 15:22:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/houthis-ramp-up-attacks-on-ships-in-red-sea-with-little-international-response/0000018c-6d6a-de43-affd-fd6ad2b60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队宣布三名士兵在加沙战斗中死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-announces-deaths-of-three-soldiers-in-gaza-combat/0000018c-6ddb-d798-adac-edff75360000</link><description>三名死去的以色列士兵是中士。谢伊·尤里尔·皮泽姆 (Shay Uriel Pizem) 少校，23 岁，中士。奥兹·什穆埃尔·阿拉迪 (Oz Shmuel Aradi)，19 岁，军士长。托梅尔·什洛莫·迈亚拉，28 岁</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 15:18:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-announces-deaths-of-three-soldiers-in-gaza-combat/0000018c-6ddb-d798-adac-edff75360000</guid></item><item><title>以色列边境警察在东耶路撒冷拍摄到袭击阿拉伯记者的画面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-border-police-officers-filmed-attacking-arab-journalist-in-east-jerusalem/0000018c-6da2-dbd5-a39c-fff36db10000</link><description>摄影记者穆斯塔法·哈鲁夫 (Mustafa Al-Haruf) 在东耶路撒冷瓦迪乔兹 (Wadi Joz) 社区记录周五的祈祷时遭到边防警察的袭击。两名涉事警员被停职，事件正在调查中</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 15:01:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-border-police-officers-filmed-attacking-arab-journalist-in-east-jerusalem/0000018c-6da2-dbd5-a39c-fff36db10000</guid></item><item><title>对美国武器的依赖迫使内塔尼亚胡接受拜登的战争要求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/reliance-on-u-s-weapons-forces-netanyahu-to-accept-bidens-war-requests/0000018c-6d45-dbd5-a39c-ff7706f50000</link><description>这位美国总统正试图平衡他对以色列的支持和来自他的支持者的压力，以制定以色列的战时政策。事实证明，军事援助计划是美国对以色列的最佳筹码</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 13:29:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/reliance-on-u-s-weapons-forces-netanyahu-to-accept-bidens-war-requests/0000018c-6d45-dbd5-a39c-ff7706f50000</guid></item><item><title>“几乎完全有罪不罚的环境”：英国带头呼吁以色列解决定居者暴力问题 15 个国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/britain-leads-15-nation-call-on-israel-to-tackle-west-bank-settler-violence/0000018c-6d31-d798-adac-edbf772b0000</link><description>法国、加拿大、澳大利亚等十几个国家强调，“以色列作为占领国，必须采取积极措施保护约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦平民”。西方政府正在制定旅行禁令的标准，并正在收集相关名称</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 11:57:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/britain-leads-15-nation-call-on-israel-to-tackle-west-bank-settler-violence/0000018c-6d31-d798-adac-edbf772b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军从加沙救出三具被哈马斯杀害的以色列人质尸体，其中包括两名士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/idf-rescues-three-bodies-of-hamas-slain-israeli-hostages-from-gaza-including-two-soldiers/0000018c-6cb4-de43-affd-fcb6e9450000</link><description>尼克·贝瑟、罗恩·谢尔曼和埃利亚·托莱达诺的尸体于周五被打捞并运回以色列；以色列国防军没有提供有关三名人质死亡情况的信息</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 10:03:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/idf-rescues-three-bodies-of-hamas-slain-israeli-hostages-from-gaza-including-two-soldiers/0000018c-6cb4-de43-affd-fcb6e9450000</guid></item><item><title>该营唯一的女性是拯救受伤士兵生命的医生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/battalions-only-woman-is-doctor-who-saves-wounded-troops-lives/0000018c-69f2-d798-adac-edff42660000</link><description>27 岁的丹妮拉·阿加耶夫 (Daniella Agaev) 博士对她所在的营至关重要，她并不关心自己是团队中唯一的女性。自十月地面行动开始以来，她几乎没有离开过加沙，并拯救了许多战友的生命</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 04:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/battalions-only-woman-is-doctor-who-saves-wounded-troops-lives/0000018c-69f2-d798-adac-edff42660000</guid></item></channel></rss>